{"tid":165772,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪只要一方有感情 就連朋友都唔可以做？","createTime":"2017-03-21T15:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T12:15:42.000Z","uid":76284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"284c4e4a13e4175eb687628ac73ac27353ba1ace","tid":165772,"uid":76284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"話說有個friend左一段時間既人 突然間話鐘意我<br />\n因為我對佢冇feel 所以我拒絕左佢<br />\n但friend就完全冇問題<br />\n我唔想佢覺得我唔鐘意佢就連friend都唔係<br />\n咁樣既話大家都會冇左個朋友<br />\n但有感情既佢 應該暫時都係嬲左我咁既款<br />\n可唔可以話我知<br />\n應該點做<br />\n係咪連朋友都冇左<br />\n利申： 非收兵 好忙唔想拍拖著"},{"pid":"64ae6608ba3fe2417cfa97c7d3a5ca3c2c76d3dc","tid":165772,"uid":30926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"聽日搵返佢 照平時咁相處模式應該okay"},{"pid":"62e2a5729b57453649d9e476cabc27161cc00b30","tid":165772,"uid":76284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日搵返佢 照平時咁相處模式應該okay</blockquote><br />\n但佢好似好尷尬咁"},{"pid":"011ea865783de742b99d70198db036f07d6f4545","tid":165772,"uid":85902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽日搵返佢 照平時咁相處模式應該okay</blockquote><br />\n但佢好似好尷尬咁</blockquote><br />\n但你唔理佢 其實仲尷尬 分明避佢咁"},{"pid":"ac6b287cf735dbab627c7e33d12221cfd5965009","tid":165772,"uid":92194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1e3a65ab1f50d30faa563c28f0ba60fa2036a6","tid":165772,"uid":45678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"68a6647ef019ebb08760fb7f76848e7615dea3ed","tid":165772,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n<br />\n不過通常都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人好撚小器"},{"pid":"92a6e5398f829038cddb615ebb8a2c1d65cc373d","tid":165772,"uid":55620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"人人唔同 不過我係<br />\n之前聽佢身邊啲好朋友話去馬<br />\n點知衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n為左令自己忘記佢我block哂佢所有野<br />\n其實佢話可以繼續做好朋友 <br />\n不過我接受唔到<br />\n原本大家感情極好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇後悔咁做"},{"pid":"b2abc1dd1f474dfdaadf3cfce4e89b849108d284","tid":165772,"uid":92194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人人唔同 不過我係<br />\n之前聽佢身邊啲好朋友話去馬<br />\n點知衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n為左令自己忘記佢我block哂佢所有野<br />\n其實佢話可以繼續做好朋友 <br />\n不過我接受唔到<br />\n原本大家感情極好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇後悔咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<br />\n我係暗戀咗佢兩年 <br />\n一路都唔敢表白<br />\n幾個月前佢同人拍咗拖<br />\n情人節前佢仲當面問我送咩禮物好<br />\n嗰刻真係生不如死<br />\n仲要扮冇野俾意見佢<br />\n諗返都覺得自己犯賤<br />\n之後我返到去刪哂佢所有野"},{"pid":"ed1e5ef73b0f20bd8df811b09c1d5b265789cbbc","tid":165772,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"你回答佢?"},{"pid":"1c05245af9a42e19404d7eff6d830281b0ebcd9c","tid":165772,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你點答佢?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898dad09fb0e44966875877d94abfe7f90ad99a1","tid":165772,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n<br />\n只要一方投放左感情<br />\n<br />\n唔會做到好朋友<br />\n<br />\n所以男女係無純友誼"},{"pid":"33643dce7ad6a4684d226facb42d527ec7251f82","tid":165772,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"你無野可以做到令佢同返你做朋友<br />\n因為佢可能已經block哂你所有野<br />\n除非你揀同佢一齊 <br />\n利申:我經歷過N次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奉勸放棄呢個fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272d15e5d9b05880e2e99b32c33cf578ce67e0e3","tid":165772,"uid":61818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"仲唔unfrd你 唔通見證你結婚生仔  之後用好朋友身份祝賀你  咪傻"},{"pid":"67db5666fa7b94cbfa83c20729339976ce1f19de","tid":165772,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"其中一個忍唔住表白就冇朋友做架喇"},{"pid":"b76b2318ff67881f9fc16632714d7aaa7db9131a","tid":165772,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"繼續做朋友 佢都唔會當你係朋友 <br />\n甚至覺得自己仲有機 然後不斷對你好 <br />\n你唔收兵佢都會自動做兵咁對你好"},{"pid":"e036c088de80e52fc7d2f842f55050bfd110909e","tid":165772,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"有左感情就唔得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有感情係冇純友誼架啦    仲做到友誼 一係條仔覺得仲有機 唔放棄 或者 已經轉移時線溝其他  或者條女想收兵"},{"pid":"53c6bd35b54290a70d1df339e1637c87e5879282","tid":165772,"uid":61818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"哩d男人唔係小器  係深明愛人要結婚 新郎不是我"},{"pid":"3452c12b72278ca9d2f0e658c9a10a70e26fc1ad","tid":165772,"uid":55620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哩d男人唔係小器  係深明愛人要結婚 新郎不是我</blockquote><br />\n冇錯 反而我唔明點解唔離開  一係佢係狗厹完全唔當一件事 眼白白望住自己鍾意既人同第2個果種感覺好痛苦"},{"pid":"1aa188469a782cf73e9080e332813e171a57b493","tid":165772,"uid":55620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哩d男人唔係小器  係深明愛人要結婚 新郎不是我</blockquote><br />\n冇錯 反而我唔明點解唔離開  一係佢係<span style=\"color: red;\">厹</span>完全唔當一件事 眼白白望住自己鍾意既人同第2個果種感覺好痛苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"aca3ab35fc6aaf0ae3ac56788ea845e689e5c8e1","tid":165772,"uid":33555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"真係寧願fd都唔做<br />\n<br />\n唔通明明愛你但仲keep住做fd<br />\n到你拍拖仲要笑笑口咁祝福你<br />\n咁好慘啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ded2775238251f30ea7b2cfa3cc60de3b97a46e","tid":165772,"uid":1558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:58:55.000Z","msg":"係，起碼當下呢一刻已經無朋友做<br />\n你想做朋友，但佢繼續留係你身邊都唔甘心只係朋友，到時情況就如同收兵，因為佢會繼續努力，繼續以「朋友」身分對你最好同付出，到時佢只會愈來愈痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左一年半載，佢放低左就可能有機會做返朋友"},{"pid":"15abadb5f358850282a607aa1d1a2151411dbecb","tid":165772,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"講清楚就可以"},{"pid":"2305f34b826c2d1b379fab806d976e1e718181dd","tid":165772,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"9996e33af0984dc436ed657ba85ccebb028e80f8","tid":165772,"uid":64920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"你放過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}